QUALITY OF LIFE; MEDICAL COSTS; MINORITIES -- HEALTH; BLACKS -- HEALTH; 
HISPANICS -- HEALTH; INDIGENTS; WEALTHY PEOPLE; HEALTH STATISTICS 
</P>
