<P>
DEPARTMENT OF DEFENSE (U.S.) -- BUDGET; DEFENSE SPENDING; UNITED STATES -- 
ARMED FORCES; MILITARY EQUIPMENT AND SUPPLIES; GOVERNMENT PROPERTY; SURPLUS 
PROPERTY; STORAGE; HOARDING 
</P>
