at the Phoenix House drug treatment center in Santa Ana. ; Photo, At left, 
Carol Olds, 31, has been at the Phoenix House for 5 1/2 months.; Photo, At 
right, William H. Smith, director of clinical services at the care center. MARK 
BOSTER / Los Angeles Times 
